User Manual

Power Switch:
    Down: Off
    Up: On

Shutter Button:
  Press and hold to start recording
  (Note: There may be a short delay before recording begins)
    LED bright: Recording is in progress
    LED dim: Recording is being saved
    LED off: Camera is in standby mode

Charging the Battery
  Connect a USB-C cable with a phone power adapter to the USB-C port.

  Red Battery LED (next to the USB-C port):
    Off: Battery is fully charged
    Solid on: Battery is charging
